wsu-wsu-batch-contents: Help message for a form input
wsu-wsu-error-linetooshort: Error message. $1 is a line number
wsu-wsu-error-noqualifiers: Error message. Refers to Wikbiase statement qualifiers
wsu-wsu-error-onlyq: Error message. Refers to Wikibase Q-items.
wsu-wsu-error-unsupportedcommand: Error message. Command means of property, label, description, alias or sitelink.
wsu-start: Button label that queues updates to the jobqueue
wsu-stop: Button label that ensures all future jobs are stopped for given batch.
wsu-command-P: Table cell value. Property as in Wikibase property.
wsu-batchtable-subject: Table column header. Subject as in Wikibase item.
wsu-batchtable-command: Table column header. Command means one of property, label, description, alias or sitelink.
wsu-batchtable-id: Table column header. Either property number or language code or sitelink code.
wsu-batchtable-value: Table column header. Value of a property in the input.
wsu-batchtable-status: Table column header. Status of the update process for a row.
